Company Overview of Stillwater Investment Management, L.P.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Stillwater Investment Management, L.P. is a privately owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm invests in the public equity markets. Stillwater Investment Management, L.P. is based in Palo Alto, California.


524 Hamilton AvenueSuite 200Palo Alto, CA 94301-2011United States



Phone: 650-437-0630

Fax: 650-437-0619

www.stillwaterim.com







