				Portfolio Management				
Stillwater Investment Management specializes in constructing actively managed, balanced investment portfolios for our clients. A thoughtful, balanced approach to investment management focuses on three primary objectives:
• Preservation of capital
• Regular income
• Long-term growth of principal
We are interested in achieving a competitive return given a comfortable level of risk. Management of portfolio risk is central to a balanced approach and is achieved by broadening the scope of investment choices to a wide range of securities.




Stillwater Investment Management specializes in constructing actively managed, balanced investment portfolios
for our clients.








“We are interested in achieving a competitive return given a comfortable level of risk.”






